name: geoana
raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: "0.8.0"
  # ensure is_freethreading gets detected as a used variable
  touch_is_freethreading: ${{ is_freethreading }}

package:
  name: geoana
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/g/geoana/geoana-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fd468dd6d7d6532235fbfb68d5b1651ea648a0f6f9cd4a827aa85ea7613dc144

build:
  number: 0
  skip: match(python, "<3.11") or (match(python, "=3.14") and linux and is_freethreading and (aarch64 or ppc64le))

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - cython
        - numpy
        - ninja
        - pkg-config
        - meson-python
    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - meson-python
    - ninja
    - pkg-config
    - python
    - python-build
    - cython
    - numpy
    - setuptools_scm >=6.2
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.22
    - scipy >=1.12
    - libdlf

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - geoana
        - geoana.earthquake
        - geoana.em
        - geoana.kernels._extensions

about:
  homepage: https://www.simpeg.xyz
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Interactive geoscience (mostly) analytic functions.
  repository: https://github.com/simpeg/geoana
  documentation: https://geoana.simpeg.xyz

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lheagy
    - jcapriot
